WEBVTT

01:38.030 --> 01:40.979
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.070 --> 01:43.979
[Episode 1]

02:13.030 --> 02:13.360
[Honey]

02:14.240 --> 02:14.870
[Video call]

02:14.870 --> 02:15.610
[Video call] [Voice call]

02:16.150 --> 02:17.150
[Honey]

02:24.780 --> 02:26.840
[Ubstan]

02:37.810 --> 02:40.210
[Honey]

02:58.070 --> 02:59.860
[Svelto Hotel Group]

03:16.120 --> 03:17.280
Hello.

03:18.000 --> 03:19.400
May I have your room card?

03:20.079 --> 03:21.240
Let me show you the way.

03:21.240 --> 03:21.870
Here.

03:22.280 --> 03:23.120
May I help?

03:23.120 --> 03:24.150
Perfect angle.

03:24.150 --> 03:24.710
Here.

03:25.470 --> 03:26.150
Hope you like it.

03:26.150 --> 03:26.750
Kenny.

03:27.000 --> 03:29.280
The supplier wants to raise the price
again.

03:29.280 --> 03:29.870
How come?

03:30.400 --> 03:32.910
Rati's current quote
is one percent higher than ours.

03:32.910 --> 03:34.370
They won't work with Rati.

03:34.840 --> 03:36.079
There's been chaos

03:36.079 --> 03:37.150
in Rati's quorum.

03:37.150 --> 03:38.750
Half the businesses have collapsed.

03:38.750 --> 03:41.680
They can't even take a decent target
for their gloss.

03:41.680 --> 03:42.430
Gotcha.

03:45.750 --> 03:47.120
It's gonna be a busy day?

03:47.120 --> 03:48.710
As long as it's a happy day.

03:49.800 --> 03:50.730
Move on. Move on.

03:51.400 --> 03:52.630
Go. Go. Go.

04:16.720 --> 04:17.480
Hello, Madam.

04:17.480 --> 04:18.480
Hello, hi.

04:18.800 --> 04:20.000
I have a reservation

04:20.000 --> 04:21.510
with my husband Nie Yucheng.

04:21.510 --> 04:22.680
Here's my passport.

04:22.830 --> 04:24.270
Could you help me check in?

04:24.270 --> 04:25.930
Sure, let me check the system.

04:29.160 --> 04:30.950
The system shows that your reservation

04:30.950 --> 04:32.210
starts from tomorrow.

04:32.800 --> 04:33.310
Yes.

04:33.310 --> 04:35.830
I arrived a day earlier than planned

04:35.830 --> 04:37.890
because I want to give him a surprise.

04:38.120 --> 04:40.120
Can you help me check in today, please?

04:40.120 --> 04:42.040
Sure, let me check the room availability.

04:42.040 --> 04:42.680
Okay.

04:46.960 --> 04:48.640
[Check in Information]
[Mr. Nie Yucheng] [Mrs. Lu Zhenzhen]

04:49.310 --> 04:50.430
Is there a problem?

04:50.480 --> 04:51.409
Welcome, Madam.

04:51.430 --> 04:52.830
Anything I can do for you?

04:55.510 --> 04:57.510
I'm the general manager of this hotel.

04:57.510 --> 04:59.040
Are you here to find Mr. Nie?

04:59.710 --> 05:01.430
Have you contacted Mr. Nie?

05:01.430 --> 05:03.040
I was supposed to arrive tomorrow,

05:03.040 --> 05:04.270
but I've come a day early

05:04.270 --> 05:05.390
just to give him a surprise.

05:05.390 --> 05:06.310
I understand.

05:06.310 --> 05:07.970
Let me help you check in first.

05:09.920 --> 05:11.400
[Kenny Ji]

05:10.600 --> 05:11.950
Kenny Ji?

05:23.480 --> 05:24.510
Not the one you think.

05:24.510 --> 05:25.240
My surname is Ji,

05:25.240 --> 05:26.160
Ji as in discipline.

05:26.160 --> 05:27.070
Mr. Ji, you're so young

05:27.070 --> 05:27.720
and already

05:27.720 --> 05:30.630
the general manager
of the Svelto Hotel Group.

05:30.630 --> 05:31.560
That's really impressive.

05:31.560 --> 05:33.620
I'm just the acting general manager.

05:34.270 --> 05:35.040
Alright.

05:35.270 --> 05:36.909
Let me show you to your room.

05:37.040 --> 05:37.510
Thank you.

05:37.510 --> 05:37.970
Please.

05:41.390 --> 05:41.750
Let me.

05:41.750 --> 05:42.310
Thanks.

05:42.800 --> 05:43.360
This way.

05:45.360 --> 05:46.600
Where are my pants?

05:59.659 --> 06:00.270
Please.

06:13.480 --> 06:14.310
So stylish.

06:14.680 --> 06:16.310
Is this made of a wine bottle?

06:17.070 --> 06:18.270
All the artworks here

06:18.270 --> 06:19.220
were designed

06:19.310 --> 06:21.370
by one of our wine-loving designers.

06:21.480 --> 06:22.510
And this piece

06:22.510 --> 06:23.630
was crafted

06:23.630 --> 06:25.150
using his favorite bottle

06:25.390 --> 06:26.450
of Screaming Eagle

06:26.510 --> 06:27.510
by his own hands.

06:27.920 --> 06:29.680
This wine has a very special taste.

06:29.680 --> 06:30.560
Do you have it here?

06:30.560 --> 06:31.160
Yes,

06:31.160 --> 06:32.920
we have some limited stock.

06:53.950 --> 06:56.680
Didn't you promise
to spend the whole day with me?

07:06.070 --> 07:06.870
Honey?

07:10.630 --> 07:12.030
He's probably not up yet.

07:14.060 --> 07:15.720
Can I borrow your master key?

07:19.570 --> 07:20.320
No problem.

07:26.400 --> 07:27.000
Yucheng.

07:27.190 --> 07:27.830
Honey.

07:28.630 --> 07:30.090
Why are you here a day early?

07:30.090 --> 07:31.730
I wanted to surprise you.

07:31.760 --> 07:34.140
You're the one on a business trip
on our anniversary.

07:34.140 --> 07:35.140
Come in.

07:40.520 --> 07:41.960
Have you changed a room?

07:43.400 --> 07:44.050
Mrs. Nie.

07:44.360 --> 07:46.430
Mr. Nie is a VIP guest at our hotel.

07:46.510 --> 07:48.070
We just upgraded his room

07:48.070 --> 07:49.400
to a suite this morning.

07:49.870 --> 07:51.670
Thank you for receiving my wife.

07:51.750 --> 07:52.430
My pleasure.

07:52.430 --> 07:52.950
Well,

07:53.040 --> 07:55.159
please book a candlelit dinner
for tonight,

07:55.159 --> 07:56.120
with the premium set.

07:56.120 --> 07:57.790
I've also ordered
a bottle of Screaming Eagle.

07:57.790 --> 07:58.950
Let's open it tonight.

07:58.950 --> 07:59.680
No problem.

07:59.830 --> 08:01.240
Do you know what Screaming Eagle is?

08:01.240 --> 08:01.920
I don't know.

08:01.920 --> 08:03.720
What kind of wine is it?

08:04.360 --> 08:06.730
It's red wine with a very unique flavor.

08:07.430 --> 08:09.000
I ordered a bottle

08:09.000 --> 08:10.240
for our wedding anniversary.

08:10.240 --> 08:11.270
You're so sweet, Honey.

08:11.270 --> 08:12.000
Thank you.

08:12.820 --> 08:14.240
I'll leave you two alone then.

08:14.240 --> 08:15.120
Get some rest.

08:15.700 --> 08:16.700
I'll walk him out.

08:21.830 --> 08:23.350
Thank you for contacting me right away

08:23.350 --> 08:24.310
and changing my room.

08:24.310 --> 08:25.840
Have you contacted Mr. Nie?

08:25.910 --> 08:27.480
I was supposed to arrive tomorrow,

08:27.480 --> 08:28.750
but I've come a day early

08:28.750 --> 08:29.870
just to give him a surprise.

08:29.870 --> 08:30.720
I understand.

08:30.720 --> 08:32.380
Let me help you check in first.

08:34.690 --> 08:36.780
[Contact Mr. Nie to upgrade the room]

08:39.140 --> 08:40.140
Don't mention it.

08:53.170 --> 08:54.080
Richard.

08:54.730 --> 08:56.120
Mr. Nie and his wife

08:56.120 --> 08:58.420
have moved into the luxury suite.

08:58.480 --> 08:59.670
Make sure you take care

08:59.670 --> 09:00.930
of anything they need.

09:01.320 --> 09:02.120
You know Changyang

09:02.120 --> 09:04.550
is our important partner
we have to secure.

09:05.140 --> 09:06.940
Don't make any mistakes happen.

09:08.260 --> 09:08.900
Also,

09:09.040 --> 09:10.840
send me the proposal by tonight.

09:12.750 --> 09:14.150
The room is so spacious.

09:17.560 --> 09:19.340
Honey, you're really amazing.

09:19.480 --> 09:20.630
We get VIP treatment

09:21.360 --> 09:22.910
wherever we go.

09:22.910 --> 09:25.480
They're all doing it out of respect
for Changyang Travel.

09:25.480 --> 09:26.270
I'm guessing

09:26.270 --> 09:27.390
the hotel owner

09:27.390 --> 09:29.320
wants to enter the Chinese market.

09:51.540 --> 09:52.320
You forgot it,

09:52.320 --> 09:53.580
so I brought it for you.

09:54.360 --> 09:55.750
Actually, this would work fine too.

09:55.750 --> 09:57.320
Using our own is more reassuring.

09:57.320 --> 09:57.790
You know,

09:57.790 --> 09:58.720
when I was in school,

09:58.720 --> 10:00.670
our professor told us

10:00.670 --> 10:02.200
that many hotels

10:02.200 --> 10:03.870
would secretly reuse

10:03.870 --> 10:05.360
these disposable products.

10:05.360 --> 10:06.240
It's so unsafe.

10:06.270 --> 10:07.600
When you were in school,

10:07.770 --> 10:09.430
wasn't that over a decade ago?

10:09.510 --> 10:10.870
The internet has come such a long way,

10:10.870 --> 10:12.510
and with so many people
checking out hotels,

10:12.510 --> 10:14.510
this kind of hotel wouldn't do that.

10:14.820 --> 10:16.040
But thank you anyway.

10:34.050 --> 10:35.500
[Screaming Eagle]

10:37.050 --> 10:39.360
Where's the last bottle
of Screaming Eagle?

10:39.360 --> 10:42.220
I just checked the inventory,
and it was still there.

10:42.220 --> 10:43.550
A man just bought it.

10:44.030 --> 10:45.930
The inventory
may not have been updated yet.

10:45.930 --> 10:46.890
Oh my God!

10:47.100 --> 10:48.200
What should we do?

10:49.300 --> 10:50.550
I need this bottle.

10:51.410 --> 10:52.720
I really need this now.

11:00.300 --> 11:01.540
[Shanghai Purong Hotel
Caught in VAM Crisis]

11:01.570 --> 11:02.800
[A Time-Honored Hotel
Faces Operational Collapse]

11:02.240 --> 11:03.160
Mr. Ji,

11:03.180 --> 11:05.900
we're out of the red wine
that Mr. Nie wanted.

11:06.010 --> 11:08.160
Someone just bought the last bottle.

11:08.190 --> 11:09.530
He is Gray Tino.

11:10.140 --> 11:12.770
Do everything you can to hold on Mr. Tino.

11:12.810 --> 11:14.730
I'll be there as soon as possible.

11:14.770 --> 11:17.130
Please allow me to wrap the wine
for you, Sir.

11:17.130 --> 11:17.940
No, thanks.

11:18.770 --> 11:19.480
Mr. Tino,

11:19.480 --> 11:21.160
we won't hold you up much longer.

11:21.160 --> 11:21.840
Please let—

11:21.870 --> 11:23.510
Stop wasting my time.

11:23.580 --> 11:25.000
I'm not making a trade

11:25.000 --> 11:26.910
even if the hotel owner comes.

11:26.990 --> 11:27.630
You know,

11:27.650 --> 11:29.470
I don't have a problem with the wine.

11:29.470 --> 11:31.440
I have a problem with the service.

11:31.480 --> 11:32.840
You're trying to force me

11:32.840 --> 11:35.360
to exchange a bottle that I already own.

11:35.390 --> 11:36.910
That's disrespectful.

11:37.120 --> 11:38.600
I'm gonna leave now.

11:42.580 --> 11:43.350
[Haut-Brion]

11:43.620 --> 11:44.500
Haut-Brion.

11:44.550 --> 11:46.150
Impressive fine, Mr. Tino.

11:47.320 --> 11:48.150
This Cabernet Sauvignon

11:48.150 --> 11:50.630
is among the finest.

11:50.740 --> 11:52.460
Second, it's only second

11:52.480 --> 11:53.760
to the '82 Lafite,

11:53.790 --> 11:54.460
and

11:55.510 --> 11:58.440
it shares your birth.

11:55.600 --> 11:58.970
[Haut-Brion]

11:59.320 --> 12:01.080
1968 vintage.

12:01.100 --> 12:01.920
That's impossible.

12:01.920 --> 12:04.250
This bottle reflects our philosophy—

12:04.280 --> 12:05.310
equal respect

12:05.330 --> 12:06.990
for every guest.

12:07.240 --> 12:07.750
You may take

12:07.750 --> 12:08.610
either bottle.

12:08.910 --> 12:11.390
The choice is all yours.

12:13.850 --> 12:15.080
[Screaming Eagle]

12:18.320 --> 12:20.050
Excellent choice, Mr. Tino.

12:20.200 --> 12:21.000
You as well.

12:21.840 --> 12:22.720
So clever.

12:25.720 --> 12:27.040
This way, Mr. Tino.

12:33.910 --> 12:36.670
Honey, let's go dune bashing tomorrow.

12:37.030 --> 12:37.930
Dune bashing?

12:37.950 --> 12:40.310
I saw it on Dianjiangchun's page.

12:40.340 --> 12:41.600
She recommended

12:41.600 --> 12:43.380
a travel guide for the Ubstan area.

12:43.380 --> 12:45.980
It says dune bashing
is the top activity there.

12:48.700 --> 12:50.220
If you're busy with work,

12:50.250 --> 12:51.310
we don't have to go.

12:52.480 --> 12:53.360
It's not that.

12:54.250 --> 12:56.110
I'll check my schedule tomorrow.

12:56.680 --> 12:58.720
Our company has worked

12:58.740 --> 13:00.470
with many of these travel bloggers.

13:00.470 --> 13:02.180
They promote whatever you pay them to.

13:02.180 --> 13:04.200
Especially those with large followings.

13:04.200 --> 13:06.000
You shouldn't trust her so much.

13:08.630 --> 13:10.990
I'm working on luxury wilderness tours.

13:11.430 --> 13:12.360
How about this?

13:12.390 --> 13:14.000
I'll talk to my colleague tomorrow

13:14.000 --> 13:14.910
and have him prepare a guide

13:14.910 --> 13:15.790
for you to check first.

13:15.790 --> 13:16.510
Great.

13:16.510 --> 13:17.470
Thanks, Honey.

13:17.490 --> 13:18.420
You're welcome.

13:21.270 --> 13:22.270
Where's our wine?

13:23.630 --> 13:24.390
Right here.

13:26.670 --> 13:28.260
The red wine you ordered.

13:27.500 --> 13:28.510
[Screaming Eagle]

13:30.270 --> 13:31.150
Please allow me

13:31.150 --> 13:32.150
to open it for you.

13:37.200 --> 13:38.600
The flavor is quite nice.

13:46.550 --> 13:47.000
Mrs. Nie.

13:47.000 --> 13:47.670
Thank you.

13:48.910 --> 13:49.790
Mr. Nie.

13:49.810 --> 13:50.720
Thank you.

13:51.210 --> 13:52.540
Please savor your wine.

13:59.090 --> 14:01.820
I have a good impression
of this general manager.

14:03.830 --> 14:06.680
You're my wife,
yet on our 10th wedding anniversary,

14:06.680 --> 14:07.630
right in front of me,

14:07.630 --> 14:08.550
you compliment another man.

14:08.550 --> 14:09.390
I mean

14:09.390 --> 14:10.720
he's quite perceptive.

14:11.320 --> 14:12.270
How so?

14:12.690 --> 14:13.540
Look,

14:13.570 --> 14:14.910
it's such a big hotel.

14:15.030 --> 14:16.480
Which hotel general manager

14:16.480 --> 14:18.540
would personally come to serve wine?

14:18.600 --> 14:19.510
Unless...

14:19.510 --> 14:20.240
Unless what?

14:20.250 --> 14:21.700
Unless the guest is worth it.

14:21.700 --> 14:23.120
So you're saying

14:23.120 --> 14:24.650
he wants something from me?

14:27.720 --> 14:28.510
Listen.

14:29.810 --> 14:31.740
They've done their job quite well.

14:32.240 --> 14:32.890
Yes, yes, yes.

14:32.890 --> 14:33.370
Right.

14:33.960 --> 14:34.790
Here, Honey.

14:36.840 --> 14:38.790
Happy 10th wedding anniversary.

14:39.150 --> 14:40.150
Thank you, Honey.

14:40.400 --> 14:41.800
Happy 10th anniversary.

14:47.240 --> 14:47.640
Honey.

14:48.170 --> 14:49.750
Let's take a photo.

14:50.460 --> 14:52.370
You've been so busy with work lately.

14:52.370 --> 14:53.930
We haven't taken pictures
together for a long time.

14:53.930 --> 14:55.260
Here, give me your hand.

14:57.930 --> 14:59.290
Need any help?

15:03.960 --> 15:04.720
Thank you.

15:11.270 --> 15:11.910
Sir.

15:12.750 --> 15:14.150
You seem a bit nervous.

15:16.780 --> 15:17.370
Smile.

15:17.400 --> 15:17.930
Okay.

15:26.010 --> 15:27.090
Sorry.

15:27.130 --> 15:28.270
Have the photos been taken?

15:28.270 --> 15:29.330
Yes, they're done.

15:29.370 --> 15:30.830
Your wife is so beautiful.

15:31.080 --> 15:31.720
Thank you.

15:41.430 --> 15:42.630
It's nice to be young.

15:46.130 --> 15:46.920
Cheers.

15:50.610 --> 15:51.850
When you were young,

15:51.880 --> 15:53.150
you were much more beautiful than she is.

15:53.150 --> 15:54.360
I can tell

15:54.680 --> 15:57.010
you're complaining that I'm getting old.

15:57.150 --> 15:58.750
You're setting a trap for me.

16:00.210 --> 16:01.410
Let me see the photos.

16:19.360 --> 16:22.220
Someone as beautiful as her
can't take good photos.

16:31.000 --> 16:31.720
[Reminder of Consumer Finance Repayment]

16:31.750 --> 16:32.720
[Dear customer, your online loan payment
for this month]

16:32.750 --> 16:33.580
[is still outstanding
and will become overdue tomorrow.]

16:37.910 --> 16:38.710
What's wrong?

16:41.320 --> 16:42.240
Nothing.

16:43.120 --> 16:43.720
By the way,

16:44.000 --> 16:45.870
this hotel offers a complimentary

16:45.870 --> 16:47.550
Desert Rose Essential Oil Spa.

16:47.550 --> 16:48.590
I heard it's really good.

16:48.590 --> 16:49.680
I'd like to try it.

16:49.710 --> 16:51.950
The hotel service is that good?

16:51.600 --> 16:52.010
[On behalf of everyone at Svelto Hotel,]

16:52.010 --> 16:52.210
[we wish you a happy 10th anniversary!]

16:52.560 --> 16:54.710
Desert hot springs
are a Middle Eastern specialty.

16:54.710 --> 16:55.910
Worth giving it a try.

17:16.450 --> 17:17.819
[Pay Now]

17:19.950 --> 17:21.420
[Payment Successful]

17:32.130 --> 17:34.050
Honey, I'm back.

17:36.680 --> 17:37.550
Honey.

17:39.360 --> 17:40.560
Where are you?

17:43.570 --> 17:45.330
-Just do as I say.
-Honey.

17:45.830 --> 17:47.780
Why can't you understand what I'm saying?

17:47.780 --> 17:48.440
Hanging up.

17:51.550 --> 17:52.640
Minghui.

17:53.580 --> 17:55.240
Can't even handle a simple task.

17:55.240 --> 17:56.320
So indecisive.

17:59.250 --> 18:01.440
Did you call for turndown service?

18:01.460 --> 18:03.550
Yes, I called for turndown service.

18:03.640 --> 18:04.840
I was waiting for you.

18:10.730 --> 18:11.790
Who is it this time?

18:12.060 --> 18:13.830
It doesn't matter who it is today.

18:13.830 --> 18:15.690
You're the most important today.

18:34.410 --> 18:35.100
Wait a second.

18:35.100 --> 18:35.900
What's wrong?

18:35.950 --> 18:37.440
Something's caught in my hair.

18:37.440 --> 18:38.350
What is it?

18:39.880 --> 18:40.790
Let me see.

18:42.640 --> 18:43.440
What's wrong?

18:45.240 --> 18:46.270
What is this?

18:47.790 --> 18:50.030
Honey, you prepared this for me?

18:50.030 --> 18:51.270
This isn't mine.

18:51.690 --> 18:52.450
Not yours?

18:52.530 --> 18:53.350
Whose is this?

18:53.380 --> 18:54.590
How did it end up in your room?

18:54.590 --> 18:55.960
I have no idea.

18:55.960 --> 18:57.440
Did anyone come to the room
while I was away?

18:57.440 --> 18:58.880
Of course not.

18:58.920 --> 19:00.500
This room is newly checked in.

19:00.500 --> 19:02.100
Could it have been left
by the previous guest?

19:02.100 --> 19:03.400
The staff didn't clean properly.

19:03.400 --> 19:04.960
Didn't you notice during turndown service?

19:04.960 --> 19:06.030
The staff did the turndown service.

19:06.030 --> 19:07.590
I definitely didn't see it.

19:08.000 --> 19:08.920
No, I need to ask about this.

19:08.920 --> 19:09.440
No, don't.

19:09.440 --> 19:09.920
Call the staff.

19:09.920 --> 19:10.880
Just throw it away.

19:10.880 --> 19:12.150
No need to make a big deal out of it.

19:12.150 --> 19:13.610
This is not a small matter.

19:16.850 --> 19:18.980
Get a housekeeper to my room right now.

19:25.930 --> 19:26.780
Madam.

19:27.550 --> 19:28.810
I personally inspected this room

19:28.810 --> 19:30.290
after it was cleaned.

19:30.320 --> 19:32.330
And I'm sure it was not our staff's fault.

19:32.330 --> 19:33.710
So you think it's our fault?

19:33.710 --> 19:34.830
That's not what I meant.

19:34.830 --> 19:36.880
I wonder if you can double-check

19:36.880 --> 19:38.880
to see if it's something of your own.

19:39.420 --> 19:41.020
I'm certain this isn't mine.

19:41.200 --> 19:42.690
Let's just accept our bad luck.

19:42.690 --> 19:44.000
Have them throw it away.

19:44.000 --> 19:45.100
We can just change rooms.

19:45.100 --> 19:47.030
In a prestigious five-star hotel,

19:47.310 --> 19:48.790
a mysterious pair of underwear

19:48.790 --> 19:50.510
just appeared on our bed.

19:50.510 --> 19:52.310
Don't you find that disturbing?

19:58.210 --> 19:59.390
[Natalie]

19:59.720 --> 20:00.760
Natalie.

20:00.880 --> 20:03.030
I'm not here trying to blame anybody.

20:03.160 --> 20:05.070
We just want reassurance.

20:05.140 --> 20:07.470
I'm sure you're a competent housekeeper.

20:07.830 --> 20:09.760
But please do think carefully.

20:09.790 --> 20:10.880
During your cleaning and turndown service,

20:10.880 --> 20:12.260
did you

20:12.290 --> 20:15.960
notice this underwear at any point?

20:21.040 --> 20:21.730
Madam.

20:22.200 --> 20:23.560
Actually, this pair of underwear—

20:23.560 --> 20:24.680
Stop talking to her.

20:24.680 --> 20:25.940
She won't admit it.

20:25.970 --> 20:27.300
Why do you keep stopping me?

20:27.300 --> 20:28.580
I'm not stopping you.

20:28.950 --> 20:30.140
I mean

20:30.200 --> 20:31.310
let's call the general manager here

20:31.310 --> 20:32.310
to handle this matter.

20:32.310 --> 20:33.310
What do you think?

20:49.210 --> 20:50.140
Housekeeping.

20:53.300 --> 20:54.030
Mr. Ji.

20:54.050 --> 20:55.850
I have really checked this room.

20:59.230 --> 20:59.830
Mr. Nie,

20:59.830 --> 21:00.510
Mrs. Nie.

21:01.640 --> 21:02.790
I sincerely apologize.

21:02.790 --> 21:04.510
This is our oversight.

21:04.580 --> 21:06.790
It was caused by careless cleaning
by our staff.

21:06.790 --> 21:09.410
We will definitely
address this matter seriously.

21:09.410 --> 21:10.130
Natalie,

21:10.350 --> 21:11.910
you are no longer a housekeeper.

21:11.910 --> 21:14.160
-Mr. Ji, it's not my fault.
-Stop.

21:16.560 --> 21:17.420
Mr. Nie.

21:17.560 --> 21:19.100
Due to our inadequate service,

21:19.100 --> 21:20.950
we've caused you both
an unpleasant experience,

21:20.950 --> 21:23.450
especially
on your 10th wedding anniversary,

21:23.450 --> 21:24.650
such an important day,

21:24.650 --> 21:25.790
ruining your celebration.

21:25.790 --> 21:26.920
On behalf of the hotel,

21:26.920 --> 21:29.290
I sincerely apologize to you both again.

21:29.930 --> 21:30.590
Actually, all we need

21:30.590 --> 21:32.020
is an appropriate response.

21:32.020 --> 21:32.820
I understand.

21:33.010 --> 21:34.290
Our response

21:34.400 --> 21:36.570
is a sincere apology and compensation.

21:36.570 --> 21:38.330
I hope Mr. and Mrs. Nie

21:38.350 --> 21:40.030
will give us a chance to make it right.

21:40.030 --> 21:40.720
I wonder if you two

21:40.720 --> 21:43.000
are interested
in our desert tour activities.

21:43.000 --> 21:44.440
Such as falconry

21:44.440 --> 21:45.360
and dune bashing.

21:45.360 --> 21:46.960
We would be delighted to offer

21:46.960 --> 21:48.510
any premium experience activities

21:48.510 --> 21:50.180
to express our sincere apologies.

21:50.180 --> 21:51.580
That won't be necessary.

21:52.070 --> 21:52.830
Mr. Ji.

21:53.110 --> 21:54.640
We appreciate your sincerity.

21:54.640 --> 21:55.070
Yes.

21:55.070 --> 21:57.480
Actually, we don't want
to make things difficult for anyone.

21:57.480 --> 21:59.730
No guest
wants to encounter such situations.

21:59.730 --> 22:01.490
But since it happened,

22:01.560 --> 22:02.750
someone has to take responsibility, right?

22:02.750 --> 22:03.240
Yes.

22:04.130 --> 22:06.230
Didn't you say
you wanted to go dune bashing?

22:06.230 --> 22:07.490
I don't have any work tomorrow.

22:07.490 --> 22:08.420
I'll go with you.

22:10.680 --> 22:11.540
Thank you then.

22:12.680 --> 22:13.340
Excellent.

22:14.030 --> 22:14.640
Mr. Nie.

22:14.640 --> 22:15.650
This is my business card.

22:15.650 --> 22:17.090
It has my contact information.

22:15.940 --> 22:18.350
[Svelto Hotel Group] [Kenny Ji]
[Hotel Manager]

22:17.350 --> 22:18.510
I'll personally arrange

22:18.510 --> 22:19.750
your upcoming itinerary.

22:19.750 --> 22:21.200
Nice to meet you, Mr. Ji.

22:21.480 --> 22:22.510
Thank you for your help today.

22:22.510 --> 22:23.240
Please wait a moment.

22:23.240 --> 22:23.740
Sure.

22:30.690 --> 22:32.140
We should talk privately sometime.

22:32.060 --> 22:33.620
[Changyang Travel]

22:32.190 --> 22:33.950
It's a great pleasure to meet you,

22:33.950 --> 22:34.750
[Nie Yucheng]

22:34.040 --> 22:35.030
Director Nie.

22:35.700 --> 22:36.950
It's getting late.

22:37.000 --> 22:37.690
I won't disturb you both.

22:37.690 --> 22:38.890
Please get some rest.

22:42.610 --> 22:43.530
Wait.

22:45.440 --> 22:46.240
Yes, Mrs. Nie?

22:46.510 --> 22:47.580
Mr. Ji.

22:47.610 --> 22:49.400
Our complaint

22:49.720 --> 22:51.370
isn't directed at any individual.

22:51.370 --> 22:52.200
We're just fighting for

22:52.200 --> 22:54.110
the respect and rights we deserve.

22:54.110 --> 22:54.880
So,

22:54.880 --> 22:57.000
please show some mercy, Mr. Ji.

22:57.240 --> 22:57.810
All right.

22:57.810 --> 23:00.000
Mr. Ji knows how to handle this.

23:03.050 --> 23:03.800
I understand.

23:03.800 --> 23:04.680
Good night to you both.

23:04.680 --> 23:05.340
Good night.

23:12.150 --> 23:15.080
Mrs. Nie will find out the truth
sooner or later.

23:18.670 --> 23:20.400
That's not our job.

23:20.430 --> 23:21.500
We're here to serve,

23:21.500 --> 23:23.060
not to judge.

23:25.510 --> 23:26.350
Natalie,

23:26.370 --> 23:29.290
you and Tasha
are gonna swap shifts this week.

23:29.320 --> 23:31.720
Does that mean
I can still be a housekeeper?

23:31.720 --> 23:32.780
The case is closed.

23:33.270 --> 23:34.950
No need to dwell on it.

23:35.400 --> 23:36.730
Just focus on your work.

23:39.720 --> 23:42.320
I know
that Mr. Ji is fully aware of everything.

23:42.410 --> 23:42.950
Let's go.

24:52.960 --> 24:53.550
Good morning, Mrs. Nie.

24:53.550 --> 24:54.480
Good morning, Mr. Ji.

24:54.480 --> 24:55.910
How can I help you?

24:56.030 --> 24:56.590
About last night,

24:56.590 --> 24:57.440
I'm sorry

24:57.440 --> 24:59.120
for bothering you so late.

24:59.270 --> 25:01.070
No need to be so polite, Mrs. Nie.

25:03.120 --> 25:03.880
Mr. Ji,

25:03.880 --> 25:05.030
you know about my husband

25:05.030 --> 25:06.610
and the travel agency
where he works, right?

25:06.610 --> 25:07.240
Of course.

25:07.350 --> 25:09.610
I've heard a lot about Changyang Travel.

25:10.000 --> 25:10.640
Mr. Ji,

25:10.640 --> 25:12.990
are you interested
in domestic travel packages?

25:12.990 --> 25:14.830
I know my husband is currently

25:14.830 --> 25:17.310
exploring some
international luxury wilderness routes

25:17.310 --> 25:19.000
and inspecting some international hotels.

25:19.000 --> 25:20.480
If you're interested,

25:20.480 --> 25:22.160
I can have him contact you.

25:22.160 --> 25:23.110
You two could have a good chat.

25:23.110 --> 25:25.440
Thank you for the introduction, Mrs. Nie.

25:27.480 --> 25:28.640
Have you had breakfast, Mr. Ji?

25:28.640 --> 25:31.110
Would you like to get something
to eat together?

25:31.110 --> 25:32.110
Mrs. Nie,

25:32.150 --> 25:33.070
what do you want?

25:33.070 --> 25:34.270
Just say it directly.

25:34.310 --> 25:37.710
I'd like to check the surveillance footage
outside our room.

25:40.960 --> 25:42.210
I'm sorry, Mrs. Nie.

25:42.350 --> 25:43.550
The hotel has a policy

25:43.720 --> 25:45.700
that surveillance footage
is not available to guests.

25:45.700 --> 25:47.300
Can't you make an exception?

25:48.160 --> 25:49.480
I truly apologize.

25:50.750 --> 25:51.510
However, regarding this matter,

25:51.510 --> 25:53.200
we've already completed our investigation.

25:53.200 --> 25:53.940
What's the conclusion?

25:53.940 --> 25:56.550
It's entirely our hotel's responsibility,

25:56.590 --> 25:58.450
so you can rest assured, Mrs. Nie.

26:02.940 --> 26:04.110
Please don't misunderstand, Mr. Ji.

26:04.110 --> 26:06.960
Actually, I don't really care about
seeing the footage.

26:06.960 --> 26:08.560
I'm not the suspicious type.

26:08.560 --> 26:10.310
I trust my husband completely.

26:10.830 --> 26:13.030
You share a rock-solid relationship
with Mr. Nie.

26:13.030 --> 26:14.070
This minor misunderstanding

26:14.070 --> 26:16.550
can be considered as adding

26:16.550 --> 26:18.550
a little spice to your anniversary.

26:18.790 --> 26:20.720
We feel deeply apologetic

26:20.720 --> 26:22.780
and don't know how to make it up to you.

26:22.790 --> 26:24.270
Mr. Ji, please don't blame yourself.

26:24.270 --> 26:26.030
You manage such a large hotel

26:26.110 --> 26:27.110
and still personally attend

26:27.110 --> 26:28.270
to our small matters.

26:28.270 --> 26:29.400
We're already very grateful.

26:29.400 --> 26:30.000
Not at all.

26:30.070 --> 26:32.070
No service matter
is too small for a hotel.

26:32.070 --> 26:33.000
So, Mrs. Nie,

26:33.000 --> 26:34.920
is there anything else
I can help you with?

26:34.920 --> 26:35.920
No, thank you.

26:54.270 --> 26:54.880
Good.

26:56.070 --> 26:56.680
Mr. Ji.

26:58.440 --> 27:00.460
Thank you for your hospitality these days.

27:00.460 --> 27:02.100
My wife and I have had
a very pleasant stay.

27:02.100 --> 27:03.700
Not at all. It's my pleasure.

27:06.880 --> 27:07.480
By the way,

27:08.010 --> 27:10.350
the experience these past 2 days
has been excellent.

27:10.350 --> 27:11.750
It's definitely worth the trip.

27:11.750 --> 27:13.590
I hope your company's travel routes

27:13.590 --> 27:14.790
can be finalized soon.

27:14.790 --> 27:15.590
We're really looking forward to

27:15.590 --> 27:17.560
working with a leading enterprise
like Changyang.

27:17.560 --> 27:18.920
If you need anything,

27:18.950 --> 27:19.920
feel free to contact me anytime.

27:19.920 --> 27:20.870
Absolutely.

27:20.890 --> 27:21.600
How about this?

27:21.600 --> 27:23.680
After I get back, we'll connect

27:23.700 --> 27:25.080
and finalize the specific routes.

27:25.080 --> 27:25.660
No problem.

27:25.660 --> 27:26.290
Good.

27:26.680 --> 27:27.400
We'll be in touch.

27:27.400 --> 27:28.060
Thank you.

27:28.090 --> 27:28.590
Thanks.

27:28.590 --> 27:28.960
Let me see you out.

27:28.960 --> 27:29.510
Okay.

27:40.830 --> 27:41.480
Mr. Nie,

27:41.710 --> 27:42.440
have a safe journey.

27:42.440 --> 27:43.040
Thank you.

27:43.240 --> 27:43.770
Bye-bye.

27:45.190 --> 27:46.130
Let's go.

27:51.330 --> 27:51.860
Bye-bye.

27:52.990 --> 27:54.510
[Svelto Hotel Group]

28:01.540 --> 28:09.650
[Svelto Hotel Group]

28:05.960 --> 28:06.720
Stephen,

28:07.290 --> 28:09.610
you've been calling me
quite frequently lately.

28:09.610 --> 28:12.130
Mr. Ji, this offer is very special.

28:12.590 --> 28:13.440
You know what?

28:14.200 --> 28:15.720
By the 13th of next month,

28:16.510 --> 28:17.920
I'll have been working abroad

28:17.920 --> 28:19.510
for exactly 10 years.

28:20.160 --> 28:22.070
I'm about to be promoted
to general manager,

28:22.070 --> 28:23.750
so I won't be changing jobs.

28:27.170 --> 28:35.080
[Svelto Hotel Group]

28:37.560 --> 28:41.840
[Shanghai, China]

28:49.690 --> 28:51.230
These are really heavy.

28:52.970 --> 28:54.050
Finally home.

28:54.110 --> 28:58.000
-Low battery. Please replace.
-When I wake up,

28:58.000 --> 29:01.480
Mom teaches me English.

29:13.070 --> 29:13.720
Sister,

29:14.160 --> 29:16.110
did we come at a bad time?

29:18.830 --> 29:20.070
It's fine.

29:20.750 --> 29:21.890
These two

29:21.910 --> 29:23.260
are my younger sister

29:23.290 --> 29:25.100
and her husband.

29:25.640 --> 29:27.750
They just returned from vacation abroad

29:27.750 --> 29:29.570
and are stopping by my place to rest.

29:29.570 --> 29:31.960
You two can go rest in the bedroom.

29:31.990 --> 29:34.230
We'll be finished here soon.

29:35.960 --> 29:36.480
Okay.

29:38.480 --> 29:40.090
Sorry.

29:40.140 --> 29:41.170
It's alright.

29:41.190 --> 29:42.160
Let's continue.

29:42.820 --> 29:47.690
My father teaches me tennis
every afternoon.

29:47.720 --> 29:49.000
Let's go. Let's go.

29:49.030 --> 29:51.920
-My hobby is reading...
-Let's go.

29:52.310 --> 29:53.370
Swimming

29:53.680 --> 29:54.710
and programming.

29:55.440 --> 29:56.780
I believe

29:56.800 --> 30:02.350
reading is how I connect with the world.

30:04.640 --> 30:05.960
Man is so funny.

30:06.430 --> 30:07.880
Don't talk to me right now.

30:07.880 --> 30:09.000
I'm angry now.

30:09.740 --> 30:11.970
I know you don't want to deal with them.

30:14.210 --> 30:15.520
What happened to your hand?

30:15.520 --> 30:16.930
I was so annoyed with them.

30:16.930 --> 30:20.260
I wasn't paying attention
and got my hand caught in the door.

30:21.010 --> 30:22.720
They just invite themselves over

30:22.720 --> 30:24.520
and have been here so many times.

30:25.920 --> 30:26.610
This time,

30:26.630 --> 30:28.370
my sister really has a problem.

30:28.590 --> 30:29.830
She enrolled Man

30:29.830 --> 30:31.220
in an international school.

30:31.220 --> 30:33.420
They suddenly wanted to do a home visit.

30:33.840 --> 30:35.810
When she registered
at that international school,

30:35.810 --> 30:37.340
she put down our address...

30:41.530 --> 30:42.530
Just bear with it.

30:42.980 --> 30:43.620
She

30:44.110 --> 30:45.620
put down our home address.

30:45.740 --> 30:47.570
The teacher suddenly wanted to visit.

30:47.570 --> 30:49.230
She just needs to put on a show.

30:50.330 --> 30:52.930
But home visits
should be at their actual home.

30:53.430 --> 30:54.120
Fine.

30:54.150 --> 30:56.150
I understand putting on a show,

30:56.330 --> 30:57.710
but she could rent a place for that,

30:57.710 --> 30:58.680
couldn't she?

30:59.200 --> 31:00.130
I think

31:00.530 --> 31:02.410
your sister thinks
you're easy to take advantage of.

31:02.410 --> 31:04.160
She keeps fleecing the same sheep
over and over.

31:04.160 --> 31:05.090
And look at this,

31:05.220 --> 31:06.430
it's all a mess.

31:06.770 --> 31:09.350
Well, that's what happens
when I marry such a good husband.

31:09.350 --> 31:11.350
She's just jealous of me—

31:11.550 --> 31:13.660
jealous that I don't have to worry about
food or clothes

31:13.660 --> 31:15.500
and that you treat me so well.

31:16.830 --> 31:17.470
By the way,

31:17.790 --> 31:18.720
I'll make sure

31:18.890 --> 31:19.930
they leave soon.

31:20.050 --> 31:21.810
At most, I'll have them for dinner,

31:21.810 --> 31:24.340
but they'll definitely leave tonight,
okay?

31:24.790 --> 31:26.160
You should have

31:26.590 --> 31:28.030
at least told me about this,

31:28.030 --> 31:28.960
right?

31:29.030 --> 31:30.330
I'm sorry.

31:30.350 --> 31:31.350
I forgot.

31:34.190 --> 31:34.910
Wait.

31:36.060 --> 31:37.000
Is Yao Zhigang

31:37.000 --> 31:38.590
wearing my clothes?

31:39.010 --> 31:41.270
And is your sister wearing your clothes?

31:41.640 --> 31:42.880
Those are old clothes,

31:42.880 --> 31:44.720
and we hardly wear them anyway.

31:46.360 --> 31:46.950
Oh right,

31:47.510 --> 31:49.320
didn't I buy you a new suit jacket?

31:49.320 --> 31:50.920
Let me get it for you to try on.

31:53.990 --> 31:57.970
The new suit jacket I just bought for you.

31:58.640 --> 31:59.960
You should try it on.

32:00.880 --> 32:01.540
It's here.

32:01.870 --> 32:02.500
Come on.

32:03.650 --> 32:05.110
This suits you perfectly.

32:07.950 --> 32:08.490
Do I look good?

32:08.490 --> 32:09.250
So handsome.

32:09.960 --> 32:10.920
My husband

32:10.940 --> 32:12.000
is the most handsome,

32:12.000 --> 32:14.200
even more handsome than an Arab prince.

32:17.220 --> 32:19.080
Your home has such a great layout,

32:19.100 --> 32:20.960
and the decoration is so special.

32:21.270 --> 32:22.750
French country style.

32:23.170 --> 32:24.780
Take care.

32:32.670 --> 32:34.780
This situation

32:35.310 --> 32:36.770
is quite embarrassing.

32:37.050 --> 32:40.510
Mainly because the interview notice
came so suddenly.

32:40.540 --> 32:41.170
You know.

32:41.860 --> 32:42.720
Look at my sister.

32:42.720 --> 32:45.250
She is so quick-witted.

32:45.520 --> 32:47.720
It just left me speechless with fright.

32:47.850 --> 32:48.570
Uncle!

32:49.160 --> 32:50.790
Man. Man.

32:50.790 --> 32:51.790
Have you finished your homework?

32:51.790 --> 32:52.720
Yes.

32:52.720 --> 32:53.720
Is it correct?

32:56.000 --> 32:56.630
Yucheng.

32:56.790 --> 32:57.330
Have a seat.

32:57.330 --> 32:58.210
Let me have a word with you.

32:58.210 --> 32:59.610
Don't wrinkle your suit.

33:00.410 --> 33:01.210
What's wrong?

33:03.410 --> 33:04.540
Still no news yet?

33:05.160 --> 33:06.690
You need to try something new.

33:06.690 --> 33:07.560
The kid is right here.

33:07.560 --> 33:08.680
He doesn't understand.

33:08.680 --> 33:10.410
See how good I am to you.

33:13.560 --> 33:16.210
I found this specially for you.
It treats infertility.

33:16.210 --> 33:18.270
You can't rush these things, you know?

33:18.270 --> 33:19.400
With the right method,

33:19.400 --> 33:20.960
a little boost and you'll get results.

33:20.960 --> 33:22.220
Seven days is one course.

33:22.220 --> 33:23.110
Take it after meals.

33:23.110 --> 33:24.040
One packet a day.

33:24.070 --> 33:24.550
Got it?

33:24.550 --> 33:25.790
Okay, got it.

33:25.830 --> 33:26.790
I'll go check on Miyu

33:26.790 --> 33:27.720
-to see if she needs my help.
-You have to eat.

33:27.720 --> 33:29.120
Fine, just leave it here.

33:29.900 --> 33:31.560
It's really a secret formula.

33:34.200 --> 33:36.200
Congratulations to Kenny

33:36.220 --> 33:39.650
on winning the Svelto Hotel Group's

33:39.680 --> 33:42.960
Outstanding General Manager of the Year.

33:51.640 --> 33:53.100
Thank you so much.

33:55.160 --> 33:58.290
He's also the youngest manager

33:58.510 --> 34:00.510
in the history of the group.

34:01.000 --> 34:03.140
The most handsome one!

34:03.850 --> 34:06.340
He has earned himself

34:06.510 --> 34:09.550
a candidacy to be promoted

34:09.550 --> 34:10.840
from acting manager to general manager.

34:10.840 --> 34:13.770
Mr. Ji didn't get promoted
to general manager again?

34:15.840 --> 34:16.960
And the other candidate

34:16.960 --> 34:18.670
is Mr. Smith.

34:18.670 --> 34:21.480
Andy Smith is a specialist

34:21.480 --> 34:25.440
from the group.

34:25.440 --> 34:27.760
He's one of the best general managers
from our company.

34:27.760 --> 34:30.670
Please, let's welcome Mr. Smith.

34:32.360 --> 34:33.630
What nonsense is he talking about?

34:33.630 --> 34:35.989
Mr. Ji is the most suitable person
for the general manager position.

34:35.989 --> 34:36.780
Welcome.

34:39.480 --> 34:40.480
Mr. Smith.

34:42.150 --> 34:43.590
Just call me Andy, guys.

34:45.480 --> 34:47.780
I've got not so many rules
when you work with me.

34:47.780 --> 34:50.310
But the most important thing
is performance.

34:51.940 --> 34:53.400
It's a little harsh on you.

34:56.130 --> 34:57.410
No, thanks to you.

35:13.840 --> 35:14.710
Phil.

35:15.880 --> 35:17.320
I closed the deal,

35:17.960 --> 35:19.320
hit the KPI,

35:19.510 --> 35:21.640
and secured the Chinese partnership.

35:23.400 --> 35:25.180
You know better than anyone

35:25.590 --> 35:27.860
that you shouldn't push me out.

35:29.750 --> 35:30.940
Some doors

35:30.960 --> 35:32.110
stay closed from the beginning,

35:32.110 --> 35:33.640
regardless of the outcome.

35:34.110 --> 35:34.710
Still,

35:35.320 --> 35:37.520
I thought this time would be different.

35:37.650 --> 35:40.120
I thought you would recognize

35:40.150 --> 35:41.880
what I've brought to the table.

35:43.210 --> 35:45.000
Because you're very good.

35:46.250 --> 35:48.050
It's well-known in the company.

35:48.840 --> 35:50.110
This is a big group.

35:51.230 --> 35:54.880
We value your amazing innovatability.

35:55.190 --> 35:57.210
A young man like you

35:57.230 --> 35:58.420
is ambitious.

35:58.760 --> 36:02.420
Why are you concerned about
the title of general manager?

36:10.630 --> 36:13.880
Our next hotel is in South Africa.

36:38.070 --> 36:39.230
Sister, Zhigang,

36:39.230 --> 36:39.880
have some food.

36:39.880 --> 36:40.680
-Okay.
-Okay.

36:41.110 --> 36:41.760
Man, here.

36:41.760 --> 36:42.960
Try this salted egg yolk chicken wing.

36:42.960 --> 36:44.110
Thank you, Aunt.

36:44.550 --> 36:46.010
I'd like to toast Yucheng.

36:46.330 --> 36:47.120
Yucheng,

36:47.150 --> 36:49.210
you're the lucky star of our family

36:49.590 --> 36:51.980
and especially a benefactor
to our Zhigang.

36:51.980 --> 36:54.820
The job you arranged for Zhigang

36:55.880 --> 36:58.530
is really high pay for little work.

36:58.690 --> 37:00.730
Everyone's so jealous.

37:00.960 --> 37:02.080
I was like,

37:02.230 --> 37:04.460
"How could you compare with me?

37:04.490 --> 37:06.550
I have such a great brother-in-law."

37:07.760 --> 37:09.400
And this time,

37:09.420 --> 37:11.730
with Man's school application,

37:12.100 --> 37:13.830
we've troubled you again.

37:13.890 --> 37:15.570
But rest assured, Yucheng,

37:15.640 --> 37:17.710
it won't happen again.

37:17.840 --> 37:18.320
Here,

37:18.680 --> 37:19.820
a toast to you.

37:19.840 --> 37:21.110
We're one, no need for formalities.

37:21.110 --> 37:21.510
Good.

37:21.530 --> 37:22.790
Sorry for the trouble.

37:22.920 --> 37:24.070
It's nothing.

37:29.520 --> 37:30.850
This wine is delicious.

37:34.660 --> 37:35.370
Miyu.

37:35.480 --> 37:37.110
Did you bring back a lot of nice things

37:37.110 --> 37:39.110
from your trip abroad?

37:39.870 --> 37:42.210
I bought gifts for you guys, Mom, and Dad.

37:42.440 --> 37:43.470
You can take them back

37:43.470 --> 37:44.350
when you leave.

37:45.880 --> 37:47.360
What time is your train?

37:47.600 --> 37:48.910
No rush for the tickets.

37:48.910 --> 37:50.110
After we wake up tomorrow,

37:50.110 --> 37:50.670
we'll buy them.

37:50.670 --> 37:52.650
-High-speed trains run frequently.
-Yeah.

37:52.650 --> 37:53.190
Very convenient.

37:53.190 --> 37:53.790
Eat more.

37:57.840 --> 37:58.840
Sister, Zhigang,

37:58.870 --> 37:59.470
I'm sorry.

37:59.480 --> 38:00.550
I'm going on a business trip tomorrow.

38:00.550 --> 38:02.210
I still have unfinished work
at the company.

38:02.210 --> 38:04.170
I need to work overtime.
Please enjoy your meal.

38:04.170 --> 38:06.630
Didn't you just return
from a business trip?

38:06.960 --> 38:08.830
Their company just started a new project.

38:08.830 --> 38:10.050
He can't afford to delay.

38:10.050 --> 38:10.820
Go on and eat.

38:10.840 --> 38:12.040
I'll go help him pack.

38:12.850 --> 38:13.780
Man, here.

38:14.090 --> 38:15.080
Have another chicken wing.

38:15.080 --> 38:16.980
-Eat more.
-Thank you, Aunt.

38:18.360 --> 38:19.500
Is he really okay?

38:20.290 --> 38:20.890
It's fine.

38:22.110 --> 38:23.070
Go on and eat.

38:23.510 --> 38:24.050
Eat.

38:24.330 --> 38:25.320
Have some soup.

38:26.380 --> 38:28.110
I won't be coming home tonight.

38:29.170 --> 38:30.130
Why?

38:30.510 --> 38:31.840
I have a business trip tomorrow.

38:31.840 --> 38:33.280
There's still a lot to do at the office.

38:33.280 --> 38:34.950
I'll be working until late at night.

38:34.950 --> 38:37.400
I'll get a hotel room near the office.

38:37.420 --> 38:40.150
I need to catch an early flight
tomorrow morning.

38:41.070 --> 38:42.530
You're not angry, are you?

38:44.150 --> 38:45.150
No, of course not.

38:46.550 --> 38:48.800
Why would I be angry?

38:50.360 --> 38:51.320
The house is crowded.

38:51.320 --> 38:52.760
I'm worried you won't be comfortable.

38:52.760 --> 38:53.800
But...

38:54.100 --> 38:55.500
It's okay. It's nothing.

38:56.450 --> 38:57.320
Don't worry.

38:58.970 --> 38:59.700
I'm leaving.

39:01.100 --> 39:01.850
Take care.

39:13.790 --> 39:17.930
[JD Cinema Zone]

39:13.860 --> 39:14.630
Look.

39:14.890 --> 39:17.290
Their cinema zone is really nice.

39:17.320 --> 39:18.150
And it's free.

39:19.570 --> 39:20.930
Why hasn't Miyu come back yet?

39:20.930 --> 39:22.090
Is she mad at us?

39:22.180 --> 39:23.360
What would she be mad about?

39:23.360 --> 39:25.490
Miyu wouldn't dare to be angry with me.

39:25.960 --> 39:27.840
She's not my father's biological daughter.

39:27.840 --> 39:29.150
He's raised her ever since she was little.

39:29.150 --> 39:31.030
She can't please us enough.

39:31.030 --> 39:31.550
For Miyu,

39:31.550 --> 39:33.110
as long as Yucheng,

39:33.200 --> 39:34.070
my parents,

39:34.090 --> 39:35.890
and I are happy,

39:36.150 --> 39:37.630
only then can she be content.

39:37.630 --> 39:38.800
Do you understand?

39:39.440 --> 39:39.960
I do.

39:44.540 --> 39:45.750
I can guarantee it.

39:45.800 --> 39:46.760
Most men

39:46.760 --> 39:50.020
have no idea what a sophisticated
gold-digger looks like.

39:50.070 --> 39:51.170
Sophisticated gold-diggers

39:51.170 --> 39:53.510
operate with subtle influence
like gentle rain.

39:53.510 --> 39:54.880
Their core weapon

39:54.920 --> 39:57.150
is precisely targeted
emotional manipulation

39:57.150 --> 39:59.270
and seamless downward adaptation.

40:23.230 --> 40:24.150
[Honey]

40:33.260 --> 40:34.250
[Honey]

40:34.540 --> 40:36.020
[Baby, please bring my usual blue shirt]

40:36.040 --> 40:37.250
[to Room 1819,
Purong Hotel at 6 tomorrow.]

40:37.280 --> 40:38.400
[No need to reply. Love you.]

41:01.570 --> 41:03.680
♪ I know at the start of every story ♪

41:04.610 --> 41:06.750
♪ They all feel somewhat the same ♪

41:08.530 --> 41:10.880
♪ Just never thought I would ♪

41:11.850 --> 41:13.760
♪ Fall for you so deeply ♪

41:15.610 --> 41:17.930
♪ Why did I have to lose myself? ♪

41:18.430 --> 41:20.570
♪ In the virtual world ♪

41:21.920 --> 41:27.440
♪ Unfinished dreams hurt the most ♪

41:26.670 --> 41:27.710
I don't work.

41:28.630 --> 41:29.840
I carefully guard

41:28.860 --> 41:30.680
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

41:29.840 --> 41:31.800
my family relationships and marriage.

41:31.260 --> 41:34.490
♪ Wandering aimlessly
through the night sky ♪

41:32.670 --> 41:35.550
Sometimes I focus on one thing
at the expense of another,

41:35.550 --> 41:37.710
but I'm trying to maintain balance.

41:36.150 --> 41:37.740
♪ Until I met you ♪

41:38.400 --> 41:40.070
As long as I have my husband's

41:38.540 --> 41:41.640
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

41:40.070 --> 41:41.840
and my family's approval,

41:42.510 --> 41:44.370
even if I feel wronged sometimes,

41:44.960 --> 41:46.400
I still feel happy.

41:47.920 --> 41:49.070
Someone asked me

41:49.150 --> 41:50.480
if it's worth it.

41:52.400 --> 41:53.110
I said

41:53.920 --> 41:55.630
it's a fair exchange.

42:17.710 --> 42:19.040
Who are you looking for?

42:25.040 --> 42:25.690
I'm sorry.

42:25.710 --> 42:26.970
I got the wrong person.

42:30.230 --> 42:30.940
Yucheng.

42:32.720 --> 42:34.050
Was she looking for you?

42:36.410 --> 42:37.890
You seem a bit nervous.

42:45.260 --> 42:46.100
Who is it?
